      *
     C           *IN95     IFEQ *OFF
     C           L1SKJY    ANDEQ*BLANK
     C           L1TKR4    ANDEQS@LOC4
     C           L1STYY    ANDEQ9999
     C           L1BMON    ANDEQ8990
