     C                     MOVE L1TKR2    S@LC02
     C                     MOVE L1TKR3    S@LC03
     C                     MOVE L1TKR4    H@LOC4
      * SCHEDULE
     C                     EXSR #BTA2
      * PREVIOUS VALUE
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN33
     C                     EXSR #PRV
      *
     C           *IN33     IFEQ *OFF
