     C           #SSET     BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     D@D
     C           @@P       SUB  1         @Q      20
     C           5         MULT @Q        @Q
     C                     Z-ADD@Q        Q       20
     C           1         DO   5         X
     C                     ADD  1         Q
     C                     Z-ADDDAT,Q     D@D,X
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     @@RRN   40
     C           *IN90     DOUEQ*ON
